parameters: Explains the core mechanisms and other valuable Informations.
Welcome to the game! First I'll exlain you the mechanic of the game.
If you encouter text passages that are too long for your taste: Use the \fiPAGE DOWN KEY\fi
To tickle the main characters you need \hc[00E1DE]Mana\hc[ffffff].
You can get \hc[00E1DE]Mana\hc[ffffff] by tickling the random appearing characters around town.
But beware! They will try to stop you!
If they get their hand on you, you will loose HP!
So better don't let this happen too often!

To defeat them: Press space bar to shoot a magical beam at them!
This will give you some \hc[00E1DE]Mana\hc[ffffff].
During the main tickle events you will have the choice between different tickle tools and even more tickle spots.
Every character has a unique tickle tool that gets used on them.
Also: A short explanation what the different text windows within the main events represent:
This one represents a thought / inner monolouge.
And this one represents text by the storyteller.
To unlock the \hc[FFA500]Endless Mode\hc[ffffff] you have to beat all main characters!
There you can tickle them for as long as you want.
And you also unlock the unique tool to use it on them as much as you want!
